newid: 2006, date: 5-MAR-1987 09:23:44.74, title: NO QUAKE DAMAGE AT CHUQUICAMATA - MINE SPOKESMAN, dateline: SANTIAGO, March 5 -, body:  The earthquake which hit northern Chile
today, registering 7.0 on the open-ended Richter scale, caused
no damage to the copper mine at Chuquicamata, a mine spokesman
said.
